Class MockDriver<Data>

These classes are intended to provide extremely simple fake objects to use when testing StorageNG classes. Methods on these classes should either:

  • throw an exception
  • implement an obvious default
  • store the input

Ideally, the methods shouldn't actually do anything, (i.e. should always throw) and should be overridden explicitly in testing.
